{"type":"assistant","message":{"content":[{"id":"toolu_vrtx_01YaLp8LvyhRQeeFzMFxy9ca","input":{"file_path":"/Users/loneyu/SelfProjects/PrizmClaw/.prizmkit/specs/023-web-button-hover-animation/context-snapshot.md","content":"# Context Snapshot — F-023: Web Button Hover Animation\n\n## Section 1 — Feature Brief\n\n**Description**: 为 Web 管理台所有按钮添加鼠标悬停时的动画过渡效果。在 public/styles.css 中为 .btn 添加 transition 和 :hover 状态的 transform/brightness 变化，提升按钮交互的视觉反馈。无后端变更。\n\n**Acceptance Criteria**:\n- Given 用户将鼠标悬停在任意按钮上, When 鼠标进入按钮区域, Then 按钮显示可见的过渡动画效果\n- Given 按钮处于悬停状态, When 鼠标离开按钮, Then 动画还原至默认样式\n- Given 按钮处于 disabled 状态, When 鼠标悬停, Then 不显示悬停动画\n\n## Section 2 — Project Structure\n\n```\npublic/\n  index.html\n  js/\n  styles.css   ← TARGET FILE\n```\n\n## Section 3 — Prizm Context\n\n- Framework: Express.js, Node.js\n- Language: TypeScript (backend), CSS (frontend)\n- No backend changes needed for this feature\n\n## Section 4 — Existing Source Files\n\n### public/styles.css (relevant .btn section, lines 112-138)\n\n```css\n.btn {\n  border: 0;\n  border-radius: 10px;\n  padding: 9px 14px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n}\n\n.btn:disabled {\n  opacity: 0.6;\n  cursor: not-allowed;\n}\n\n.btn.primary {\n  background: var(--primary);\n  color: var(--primary-contrast);\n}\n\n.btn.warning {\n  background: var(--warning);\n  color: #fff;\n}\n\n.btn.ghost {\n  border: 1px solid var(--line);\n  background: transparent;\n}\n```\n\n## Section 5 — Existing Tests\n\nNo CSS-specific tests exist. This is a pure CSS visual feature; no test file needed.\n"},"name":"Write","type":"tool_use"}],"id":"req_vrtx_011CZJSBc4wcnsHeubX6nzGz","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":463,"output_tokens":18,"cache_read_input_tokens":32155},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"f313c371-add5-4a65-b746-e54a7d606853","uuid":"63c35c74-2c31-483a-b94c-c3942da0f2b5"}
